{"type": "game", "name": "Pixel Noir", "steam_appid": 754320, "required_age": 0, "is_free": false, "dlc": [1079750], "detailed_description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>STORY:</strong></h2><br>Living on the streets of a dump like Pinnacle City, there\u2019s only two things to keep you going: <strong>A pack of cigarettes and the feeling that there\u2019s more than this.</strong><br><br><img src=\"https://steamcdn-a.akamaihd.net/steam/apps/754320/extras/ezgif-2-43ed8924e393.gif?t=1560796259\" ><br><br>There was something rotten in that rundown place. You were in over your head, but you were too proud to admit it. <strong>It was your pride that killed your partner.</strong> With the hospital burned to a crisp and nothing to exonerate you, they threw you in jail.<br><br>For ten years you were haunted by unanswered questions and unspeakable horror, frightened by what you saw, what you did - and what you could still do. Now you\u2019re scraping by as a private eye, running a business out of a crappy apartment. <strong> But a chance comes along to clear your name once and for all. </strong> With your sanity at stake, how can you afford not to take it?<br><br><img src=\"https://steamcdn-a.akamaihd.net/steam/apps/754320/extras/ezgif-2-5c7c195e9280.gif?t=1560796259\" ><br><br>Pixel Noir is a <strong>turn-based RPG</strong> set against a film noir backdrop.<br><br><img src=\"https://steamcdn-a.akamaihd.net/steam/apps/754320/extras/ezgif-2-4a092934d955.gif?t=1560796259\" ><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>GAME FEATURES:</strong></h2><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Solve a variety of mysteries as Pinnacle City\u2019s cheapest Private Eye! From missing pets to murder investigations, <strong>your detective skills will earn you either fortune or face punches.</strong><br></li><li>Fight enemies in turn-based combat. <strong>Unleash devastating combo attacks by teaming up with other heroes in your team! </strong><br></li><li>Explore Pinnacle City-- <strong>a wretched hive of scum and villainy harboring black market trade &amp; hawked by colorful characters.</strong><br></li><li>Use your <strong>investigation mode</strong> to reveal clues and over time unearth new secrets and storylines!</li></ul>", "about_the_game": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>STORY:</strong></h2><br>Living on the streets of a dump like Pinnacle City, there\u2019s only two things to keep you going: <strong>A pack of cigarettes and the feeling that there\u2019s more than this.</strong><br><br><img src=\"https://steamcdn-a.akamaihd.net/steam/apps/754320/extras/ezgif-2-43ed8924e393.gif?t=1560796259\" ><br><br>There was something rotten in that rundown place. You were in over your head, but you were too proud to admit it. <strong>It was your pride that killed your partner.</strong> With the hospital burned to a crisp and nothing to exonerate you, they threw you in jail.<br><br>For ten years you were haunted by unanswered questions and unspeakable horror, frightened by what you saw, what you did - and what you could still do. Now you\u2019re scraping by as a private eye, running a business out of a crappy apartment. <strong> But a chance comes along to clear your name once and for all. </strong> With your sanity at stake, how can you afford not to take it?<br><br><img src=\"https://steamcdn-a.akamaihd.net/steam/apps/754320/extras/ezgif-2-5c7c195e9280.gif?t=1560796259\" ><br><br>Pixel Noir is a <strong>turn-based RPG</strong> set against a film noir backdrop.<br><br><img src=\"https://steamcdn-a.akamaihd.net/steam/apps/754320/extras/ezgif-2-4a092934d955.gif?t=1560796259\" ><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>GAME FEATURES:</strong></h2><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Solve a variety of mysteries as Pinnacle City\u2019s cheapest Private Eye! From missing pets to murder investigations, <strong>your detective skills will earn you either fortune or face punches.</strong><br></li><li>Fight enemies in turn-based combat. <strong>Unleash devastating combo attacks by teaming up with other heroes in your team! </strong><br></li><li>Explore Pinnacle City-- <strong>a wretched hive of scum and villainy harboring black market trade &amp; hawked by colorful characters.</strong><br></li><li>Use your <strong>investigation mode</strong> to reveal clues and over time unearth new secrets and storylines!</li></ul>", "short_description": "Something happened that night in the hospital - something that cost you your career as a police detective, your sanity and your partner's life. Ten years later, you have the chance to put things right. Are the hallucinations that plague you a key to what happened that fateful night?", "supported_languages": "English, Spanish - Spain", "header_image": "https://steamcdn-a.akamaihd.net/steam/apps/754320/header_alt_assets_2.jpg?t=1560796259", "website": "http://www.swdtechgames.com/", "pc_requirements": {"minimum": "<strong>Minimum:</strong><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><strong>OS:</strong> Windows 7<br></li><li><strong>Processor:</strong> SSE2 instruction<br></li><li><strong>Graphics:</strong> Graphics card with DX10<br></li><li><strong>Storage:</strong> 943 MB available space<br></li><li><strong>Sound Card:</strong> DirectX compatible sound card</li></ul>"}, "mac_requirements": {"minimum": "<strong>Minimum:</strong><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><strong>OS:</strong> macOS 10.12+<br></li><li><strong>Storage:</strong> 945 MB available space</li></ul>"}, "linux_requirements": {"minimum": "<strong>Minimum:</strong><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><strong>OS:</strong> Ubuntu 12.04 LTS<br></li><li><strong>Storage:</strong> 947 MB available space</li></ul>"}, "developers": ["SWDTech Games"], "publishers": ["BadLand Publishing"], "price_overview": {"currency": "EUR", "initial": 1499, "final": 1499, "discount_percent": 0, "initial_formatted": "", "final_formatted": "14,99\u20ac"}, "packages": [222325], "package_groups": [{"name": "default", "title": "Buy Pixel Noir", "description": "", "selection_text": "Select a purchase option", "save_text": "", "display_type": 0, "